<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Climate Solutions</title>
    <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@4.12.10/dist/full.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body>
     <!-- Navbar -->
    <%- include('partials/navbar', { page: '/about' }) %>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
            <div class="hero-content text-center">
                <div class="max-w-md">
                    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Explore Climate Solutions</h1>
                    <p class="py-6">Discover innovative projects that address climate change and promote sustainability.</p>
                    <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary">View Projects</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Grid Section -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Project 2: Alternative Cement -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 border-4 border-gray-700 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_alternativecement02.jpg" alt="Alternative Cement" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Alternative Cement</h2>
                    <p>Conventional cement production is a significant source of carbon dioxide. Reformulation can reduce emissions by millions of metric tons each year.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/2" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Project 3: Bicycle Infrastructure -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 border-4 border-gray-700 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_bicycle_infrastructure.jpg" alt="Bicycle Infrastructure" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Bicycle Infrastructure</h2>
                    <p>Infrastructure is essential for supporting safe and abundant bicycle use, which curbs emissions by reducing the need for fossil-fuel-dependent transportation.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/3" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Project 4: Biomass Power -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 border-4 border-gray-700 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_biomass01.jpg" alt="Biomass Power" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Biomass Power</h2>
                    <p>Biomass feedstock can replace fossil fuels for generating heat and electricity. Perennial biomass offers a “bridge” to a clean, renewable energy future.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/4" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Project 6: Bamboo Production -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 border-4 border-gray-700 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/Solution_Bamboo01.jpg" alt="Bamboo Production" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Bamboo Production</h2>
                    <p>Bamboo rapidly sequesters carbon in biomass and soil and can thrive on degraded lands. Long-lived bamboo products can store carbon over time.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/6" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Project 7: Bioplastics -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 border-4 border-gray-700 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_bioplastics02.jpg" alt="Bioplastics" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Bioplastics</h2>
                    <p>Most plastics are made from fossil fuels, but bioplastics utilize plants as an alternative source of carbon. They often have lower emissions and sometimes biodegrade.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/7" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Project 8: Carpooling -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 border-4 border-gray-700 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_carpooling.jpg" alt="Carpooling" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Carpooling</h2>
                    <p>When people share rides in passenger vehicles through ride-sharing or similar practices, they can reduce greenhouse gas emissions per traveler.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/8" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>